22443478">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">14.</div><div id="r14" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Binder RK, Webb JG, Willson AB, et al. The impact of integration of a multidetector computed tomography annulus area sizing algorithm on outcomes of transcatheter aortic valve replacement: a prospective, multicenter, controlled trial. <em>J Am Coll Cardiol</em> 2013;62(5):431–438.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jacc.2013.04.036">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23684679/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+impact+of+integration+of+a+multidetector+computed+tomography+annulus+area+sizing+algorithm+on+outcomes+of+transcatheter+aortic+valve+replacement%3A+a+prospective%2C+multicenter%2C+controlled+trial&amp;author=RK+Binder&amp;author=JG+Webb&amp;author=AB+Willson&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=J+Am+Coll+Cardiol&amp;pages=431-438&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jacc.2013.04.036&amp;pmid=23684679">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="r15" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Achenbach S, Delgado V, Hausleiter J, Schoenhagen P, Min JK, Leipsic JA. SCCT expert consensus document on computed tomography imaging before transcatheter aortic valve implantation (TAVI)/transcatheter aortic valve replacement (TAVR). <em>J Cardiovasc Comput Tomogr</em> 2012;6(6):366–380.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jcct.2012.11.002">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23217460/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scho